name: Sandy, the short one
review: I use it every day. Put it on first thing in the morning and never again.

name: Mary Ann Revilla
review: Not too happy with the product

name: Megan
review: I like this mascara well enough. I'm usually not a fan of large mascara brushes, but this one applies cleanly, and I don't accidentally stab myself in the eye when I use it. However, I have yet to find an eye makeup remover that will take this stuff off. I haven't been wearing it very often because I don't want to go through the battle of trying to remove my eye makeup with fourteen different products at the end of the day.

name: Susie
review: Liked the way my lashes look with this product, however not easy to remove.

name: snarly carli
review: Hard to apply evenly. Flakey. Really hard to get 0ff. Makes lashes crunchy. Doesn't lengthen very much.
